Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.16,0:00:04.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ladies and gentlemen!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.51,0:00:07.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I bring you miraculous illusions \Nthat will make the night sparkle!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.77,0:00:11.62,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Tonight, I present to you one of my days off.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.34,0:00:27.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The Angel's Crown is mine tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.19,0:01:17.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Kid the Phantom Thief!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.22,0:01:22.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?! \NShine it in his face!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.36,0:01:24.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,C-Crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.68,0:01:26.19,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You're...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.85,0:01:31.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's bright!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.52,0:01:37.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,D-Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.29,0:01:39.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Inspector! There's a note on your back!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.47,0:01:40.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,When did he...?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.82,0:01:44.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,"For tonight, I bid you adieu.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.01,0:01:47.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,However, I shall return \Nnext Sunday at 8:00 pm
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.26,0:01:50.62,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,to abscond with the Angel's Crown.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.62,0:01:51.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Kid the Phantom Thief."
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.96,0:01:54.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,M-Make a monkey out of me, will he?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.10,0:02:04.04,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Still, I know that face...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.91,0:02:07.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. I'm sure of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.99,0:03:51.75,Signs - Thief Title,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1000,0)}Kaito Kuroba's Busy Day Off
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.75,0:03:56.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Stare...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.97,0:04:19.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Both of you, stop eating so sullenly!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.74,0:04:23.07,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The least you could do is tell me\N if the food is any good!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.78,0:04:26.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If it wasn't any good, it's not like \NI could just come out and say it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.41,0:04:29.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So you're trying to tell me\N it isn't any good!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.93,0:04:33.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, your hamburger steaks always...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.48,0:04:34.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Look!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.94,0:04:38.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,They always crumble into little bitty pieces!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.44,0:04:41.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's an awful thing to say! \NAfter I cooked dinner for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.17,0:04:44.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna tell Chikage-san what you said!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.31,0:04:47.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, do I have something on my face?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.93,0:04:51.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Kaito, you're like a little kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.89,0:04:54.91,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.91,0:04:56.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,N-N-Nothing...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.62,0:04:58.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.78,0:05:00.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you've still got food on your plate!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.89,0:05:02.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll have it for breakfast tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.90,0:05:06.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Jeez. What's he talking about, \N"crumbling into pieces"?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.68,0:05:10.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You two are like a married couple.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.90,0:05:11.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't say that!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.66,0:05:14.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What makes me seem like\N that jackass's wife?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.77,0:05:17.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me you two \Ngo out on dates?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.74,0:05:20.42,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Of course not!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.42,0:05:24.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What, you're suspicious of us, Dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.17,0:05:26.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So that's why you were \Nstaring at Kaito tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.66,0:05:27.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.46,0:05:30.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Then why?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.00,0:05:31.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaito-kun is...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.68,0:05:33.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaito is...?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.16,0:05:35.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...Kid the Phantom Thief!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.80,0:05:41.57,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's just silly!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.57,0:05:44.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'm sure of it. I saw his face!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.21,0:05:48.57,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And Kaito-kun performs magic, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.57,0:05:49.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,All the more suspicious...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.45,0:05:52.82,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Dad...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.82,0:05:58.59,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Kid the Phantom Thief's note claims he'll \Nappear again next Sunday. I'll prove it then.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.59,0:06:00.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.65,0:06:04.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way Kaito is \NKid the Phantom Thief!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.50,0:06:05.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,On what grounds?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.47,0:06:07.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Grounds?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.84,0:06:09.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,After all, Kaito is...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.84,0:06:11.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaito-kun is what?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.64,0:06:16.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...going on a date with me next Sunday!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.93,0:06:27.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,W-W-What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.77,0:06:30.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! Are you gonna \Nmake me say it again?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.74,0:06:33.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Go on a date with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.38,0:06:36.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this? Some kind of gag?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.20,0:06:39.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you accept or not?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.48,0:06:43.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Who would go out on a \Ndate with a dog like you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.66,0:06:49.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I know... I know that...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.10,0:06:53.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But please!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.84,0:06:57.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.14,0:07:00.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?! Then let's make it next Sunday!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.52,0:07:02.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,At Tropical Land!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.86,0:07:04.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a promise!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.74,0:07:08.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Wait a second!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.86,0:07:11.11,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,I shall return next Sunday at 8:00 pm
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.14,0:07:15.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sunday's when I'm supposed to appear...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.60,0:07:18.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe {\i1}you{\i0} asked {\i1}him{\i0}\N out on a date, Aoko!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.93,0:07:21.89,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You must really like Kaito-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.89,0:07:23.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,As if I like that jerk!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.63,0:07:26.57,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't do it because I {\i1}want to{\i0}\N go on a date with him!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.28,0:07:30.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's my dad...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.76,0:07:34.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. This is Dad's fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.14,0:07:37.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Suspecting Kaito of being \NKid the Phantom Thief...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.02,0:07:40.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not possible... right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.35,0:07:43.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You were peeping in the girls' locker \Nroom again, weren't you, Kaito-kun?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.52,0:07:44.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Gulp!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.43,0:07:45.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You pervert!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.73,0:07:48.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You shouldn't use such a cheap lock!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.62,0:07:57.09,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like I was peeping.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.09,0:08:01.08,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard somebody saw a rat, so I thought \NI'd hunt it down for you, is all!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.08,0:08:02.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Come back here!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.36,0:08:03.67,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You're{\i0} the rat!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.00,0:08:07.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He {\i1}is{\i0} suspicious...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.92,0:08:10.17,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,Blue Parrot
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.71,0:08:12.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The inspector suspects you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.17,0:08:14.09,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.09,0:08:18.62,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I think he saw my face when \NI was on the job last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.62,0:08:22.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He was staring at me all \Nthrough dinner this evening.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.41,0:08:23.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.11,0:08:27.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And maybe it's not only him, \Nbut Aoko, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.98,0:08:28.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Aoko-san too?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.14,0:08:33.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,After all, she suddenly insisted \Nthat we go on a date next Sunday!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.92,0:08:36.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Next Sunday is when...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.24,0:08:39.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...I said I'd steal the Angel's Crown!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.00,0:08:44.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. I'd be careful if I were you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.48,0:08:48.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,They say there's nothing scarier \Nthan a woman's intuition.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.46,0:08:51.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a pretty heavy remark \Ncoming from you, Jii-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.46,0:08:52.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you speaking from experience?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.84,0:08:55.89,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll tell you about it someday.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.68,0:09:01.62,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,More importantly, Young Master,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.62,0:09:07.08,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I've prepared the props you requested \Nfor your next magic show.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.08,0:09:08.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.33,0:09:10.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And this, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.11,0:09:12.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.74,0:09:18.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Gotcha.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.24,0:09:22.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,With that, you should be able \Nto make it through the night.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.34,0:09:26.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I just hope I can pull it off.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.13,0:09:31.07,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Dad, what do you think I should do?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.12,0:09:39.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen, Kaito,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.85,0:09:41.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,and listen well.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.79,0:09:46.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,As the famous magician Al Baker once said,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.24,0:09:49.81,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,"Don't run away before they chase you."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.81,0:09:52.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,"Don't run away before they chase you"?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.58,0:09:53.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What does that mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.73,0:09:58.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If given a chance, the audience \Nwill begin to doubt us magicians.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.33,0:10:02.86,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,However, if you fear their gaze, \Nyou'll definitely make a mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.41,0:10:08.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A first-rate magician never \Nfears being scrutinized.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.48,0:10:10.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.10,0:10:12.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You can trust in your own ability.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.88,0:10:15.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you understand, Kaito?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.36,0:10:18.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Loud and clear, Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.65,0:10:21.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter what happens, \NI won't lose my nerve.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.65,0:10:26.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,After all, I'm the son of Kaito Toichi,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.26,0:10:28.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,the greatest phantom thief in the world!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.37,0:10:43.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaito's late...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.58,0:10:52.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay. Aoko doesn't suspect me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.83,0:10:55.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,"Don't run away before they chase you."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.23,0:10:58.42,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,All I have to do is act normally.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.61,0:11:00.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hi!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.00,0:11:03.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry to make you wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.51,0:11:08.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaito...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.53,0:11:12.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew you would come.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.75,0:11:15.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I promised, didn't I? Idiot...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.73,0:11:24.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.45,0:11:26.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.61,0:11:32.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Look! Those elephants are amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.68,0:11:33.67,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.67,0:11:35.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,They're robots.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.29,0:11:36.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.66,0:11:38.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The elephants are welcoming you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.87,0:11:42.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.05,0:11:46.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You people will never leave this room again.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.40,0:11:51.81,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The painting is stretching!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.60,0:11:56.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The room is just being lowered.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.76,0:11:58.32,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.78,0:12:01.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome to Tropical Land!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.28,0:12:05.07,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,How cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.52,0:12:08.67,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You smell sweaty!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.68,0:12:11.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaito...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.30,0:12:16.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.83,0:12:19.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait up!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.43,0:12:23.82,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you being so mean?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.82,0:12:25.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Look at me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.73,0:12:28.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.23,0:12:36.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Now that's the Aoko I know. \NThis way is more natural.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.37,0:12:43.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.93,0:12:47.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, right! You were just being mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.44,0:12:48.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Why, you...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.06,0:12:51.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Nyaah!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.67,0:13:01.81,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,D-Dumbass! You gotta eat fish \Nright in front of me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.81,0:13:04.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What can I say? I like it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.40,0:13:08.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Take that!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.61,0:13:10.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll get you for that!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.03,0:13:18.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't wait to see it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.94,0:13:22.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's almost time for me \Nto put in an appearance.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.13,0:13:23.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the perfect chance to slip away.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.18,0:13:28.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The movie's 40 minutes. \NAs long as I'm back by the end...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.24,0:13:31.82,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, 3D movies give me a headache.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.82,0:13:33.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll wait outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.96,0:13:35.08,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.04,0:13:39.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.84,0:13:45.09,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Stay with me... for just a little bit longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.09,0:13:47.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Aoko...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.31,0:13:48.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, let's watch the movie!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.33,0:13:52.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Does she know about my other identity?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.84,0:13:56.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So the inspector {\i1}did{\i0} see my face then.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.60,0:13:58.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so excited!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.97,0:14:02.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Chill out. Have faith in your own ability.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.41,0:14:18.67,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And now, please enjoy {\i1}Adventures{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.38,0:14:27.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He should be here in ten \Nminutes! Stay focused!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.60,0:14:29.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I've got 34 minutes!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.93,0:14:34.81,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That much time to do the job and get \Nback by Aoko's side! I've gotta make it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.45,0:14:38.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,One more minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.13,0:14:40.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, do you know where the inspector went?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.66,0:14:41.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.71,0:14:53.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm sleepy...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.46,0:15:07.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up! You've got 18 minutes!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.68,0:15:17.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Inspector?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.68,0:15:21.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You walked right into it, \NKid the Phantom Thief!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.10,0:15:28.19,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You walked right into my trap! \NAnd now I'll reveal your true identity!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.69,0:15:31.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And now I'll expose...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.32,0:15:33.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...your real identity!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.95,0:15:38.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A-Aoko!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.04,0:15:46.59,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,My true identity is... Captain Japan!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.78,0:15:52.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a master of disguise!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.72,0:15:55.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I can look like anyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.22,0:16:01.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Inspector Nakamori, I know \N{\i1}everyone{\i0} who's close to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.26,0:16:04.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Then you impersonated \NKaito-kun last time...?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.73,0:16:10.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And I think I'll be {\i1}you{\i0} next time,\N Inspector Nakamori.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.42,0:16:15.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,See you, Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.46,0:16:25.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Why, you...!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.49,0:16:28.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Get him!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.99,0:16:33.89,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Crap! That ate up too much time!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.89,0:16:35.87,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The movie's gonna be over in nine minutes!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.87,0:16:40.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If I'm not back by then, \NAoko will realize I'm Kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.39,0:16:44.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the end of you, Captain Japan!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.40,0:16:52.57,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Three minutes!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.96,0:16:56.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll show you my true power!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.97,0:17:01.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,90 seconds!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.12,0:17:03.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And it's two kilometers away!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.70,0:17:05.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't make it in time!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.33,0:17:07.46,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,Tropical Land Map
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.46,0:17:09.16,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,3D Movie Adventures
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.48,0:17:12.96,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,You Are Here
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.48,0:17:12.96,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,Dragon Coaster Waiting Area
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.44,0:17:15.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Dragon Coaster...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.68,0:17:19.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Turbo Beam!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.01,0:17:22.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's it! Get him!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.47,0:17:24.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! Get 'im!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.49,0:17:27.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Enjoy the ride!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.75,0:17:36.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,30 seconds!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.38,0:17:48.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Wait a second...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.18,0:18:10.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.60,0:18:56.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wasn't that exciting?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.66,0:18:58.81,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.32,0:19:06.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Dad?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.16,0:19:07.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Inspector Nakamori,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.16,0:19:16.05,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,Metro police fail to capture \NKid the Phantom Thief again...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.98,0:19:09.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, just on TV...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.49,0:19:10.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,what can you tell us about tonight's theft?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.96,0:19:13.08,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you watching this, \NKid the Phantom Thief?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.08,0:19:16.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I swear I'll arrest you next time!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.57,0:19:17.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.33,0:19:22.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaito, you're just Kaito, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.66,0:19:25.08,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait here a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.01,0:19:35.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So to prove my innocence, Aoko,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.16,0:19:38.57,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,you put me through the wringer.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.45,0:19:46.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.75,0:19:48.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Your favorite ice cream.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.76,0:19:51.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't act out of character!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.16,0:19:56.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if this isn't like me, I'm {\i1}me{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.62,0:20:02.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Jeez, you're so cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.00,0:20:04.09,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Like ice cream!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.86,0:20:15.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But ice cream...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.15,0:20:19.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...is sweet.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.69,0:20:39.59,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaito, Aoko-chan told me what you said.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.05,0:20:43.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That was a very cheesy line.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.63,0:20:45.89,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What are you talking about?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.27,0:20:50.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,"But ice cream is sweet."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.89,0:20:56.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I-It wasn't {\i1}that{\i0} bad...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.48,0:20:58.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't help it. It's funny.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.98,0:21:02.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You've reached the age where \Nyou say things like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.50,0:21:04.57,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Quit bustin' my chops, Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.57,0:21:09.09,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That reminds me of the first time \Nyour father and I went on a date...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.09,0:21:11.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,More of your nostalgia?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.39,0:21:12.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Gimme a break!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.34,0:21:14.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It was on the Champs-Élysées in Paris.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.77,0:21:18.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Your father made reservations \Nat a very fancy restaurant...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.20,0:21:24.08,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Mom, sorry to interrupt, but there's \Na show I wanna catch on TV.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.08,0:21:25.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Can we wind this up?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.29,0:21:28.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen to me! I'm almost done.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.73,0:21:31.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I doubt that very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.21,0:21:34.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Talk to you soon. Goodnight!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.06,0:21:37.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Everything has to be \Ndone at your pace, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.78,0:21:39.62,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Who do you get that from?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.62,0:21:41.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,From you, Mom, from you...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.66,0:21:44.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So anyway, at that restaurant,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.52,0:21:46.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,the wine was the finest I'd ever tasted...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.56,0:21:54.82,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, let's meet again \Nunder the sweet night sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.44,0:21:58.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,See you next illusion!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.13,0:23:34.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,For some reason, schools at night \Nhave a really creepy atmosphere.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.92,0:23:39.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But even though everyone's like, \N"There's a ghost!", I don't take it seriously.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.28,0:23:42.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So this Phantom will get to \Nthe bottom of that ghostie!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.50,0:23:45.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's childish to try and \Nexpose a ghost story?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.44,0:23:49.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, see for yourself and decide \Nwhether I'm a kid or an adult!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.65,0:23:53.78,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,Adult's Charm
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.65,0:23:53.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time on {\i1}Magic Kaito 1412{\i0}:\N Adult's Charm!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.78,0:23:56.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Step right this way! Watch carefully!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.74,0:23:58.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't miss the illusion!
